601
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:04,840
So, how is it?
You in?

602
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:12,360
Such a plane isn't cheap.

603
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,000
She said

604
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,079
if you do it well,

605
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,280
