Everyone sit.

666
00:40:56,039 --> 00:40:56,360
Sit down.

667
00:40:56,519 --> 00:40:57,639
Have some nuts.

668
00:40:58,079 --> 00:40:59,320
Eat, eat. Sit, sit.

669
00:40:59,719 --> 00:41:00,760
Sit down.

670
